<emphasis id="0FB0CA19DE6DFF98D5B8F975FC439886" box="[903,937,1754,1775]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="211">Cm</emphasis>
median tip of conductor, 
<emphasis id="0FB0CA19DE6DFF98D297F975FB299886" box="[1192,1219,1754,1775]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="211">Co</emphasis>
