</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="3D7B160BDE6CFF99D6E1FF1AFE3D9FF9" blockId="9.[169,1227,181,400]" pageId="9" pageNumber="212">
D e s c r i p t i o n. Female 
<typeStatus id="E27FA8A9DE6CFF99D7CAFF1AFD819EB9" box="[501,619,181,208]" pageId="9" pageNumber="212">holotype</typeStatus>
. Total length 2.7, carapace 1.05 long, 0.85 wide. Carapace light brown with dark brown V-mark. Chelicerae with 3 prolateral and 2 retrolateral teeth. Chelicerae, maxillae, labium and sternum yellow. All eyes with black edging (completely encircling AME and PME, on ALE and PLE on inner margins only). Leg segments dark at top. Tibiae and metatarsi with light and dark rings. Abdomen light yellow with pattern obscured due to poor specimen preservation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3D7B160BDE6CFF99D694FE1CFE6C9FA0" blockId="9.[171,390,435,457]" box="[171,390,435,457]" pageId="9" pageNumber="212">Length of leg segments</paragraph>
